      • testScrollableMoveToCurrentRow

        public void testScrollableMoveToCurrentRow()
                                    throws java.sql.SQLException
        Tests that the cursor can be positioned on the current row multiple times on a scrollable resultset.

        The motivation for the test is that the locators assoicated with the current row must not be released multiple times.

        Throws:
        java.sql.SQLException
